n Friday, January 24th, they have developed the first Stardust nanopowder to erase the virus and have spread it towards the surface of the planet from their ships stationed in Low Earth Orbit. The virus has reacted to the nanodust and mutated into a slightly less lethal and slightly more transmissible form.<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n昴宿星人正在為了阻止疫情而努力不懈地工作。他們在1月24日上星期五開發出用來消滅病毒的第一代星塵奈米粉末。他們利用駐紮在近地軌道的船艦向地表世界噴灑星塵粉末。病毒跟奈米粉末起反應之後突變成致死率較低，傳染力也稍微變強的品種。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nLearning from the reaction of the virus, the Pleiadians have developed a more advanced version of Stardust and applied it on Monday and Tuesday (January 27th and 28th).<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n昴宿星人得知病毒的反應之後便開發了更先進的星塵粉末並且在這禮拜一和禮拜二（1月27日和28日）開始對地表世界噴灑新一代的星塵粉末。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nAs as result of this, the virus is not spreading anymore with geometric progression as it was until now, and appears to be slowing down:<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n新一代的星塵粉末使得病毒不再用先前的傳染速度擴散。目前病毒的感染人數也有趨緩的跡象：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.golden-ages.org/2020/01/29/end-time-madness/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.golden-ages.org%2F2020%2F01%2F29%2Fend-time-madness%2F&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=f84691df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.golden-ages.org/2020/01/29/end-time-madness/</a>"},{"pid":"fdafdcad666829ff53637cbce752b3296d98af7b","tid":1855072,"uid":29643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"923ad7fee72df3f44aaac8863dcdacb66098b2d1","tid":1855072,"uid":185121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"323a2b62028d59e1c99e0bba086798cd1da22e30","tid":1855072,"uid":159876,"like":106,"dislike":0,"score":106,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T01:17:36.000Z","msg":"外星人落地球搶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T06:26:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔落咪唔洗搶囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T08:42:56.000Z","msg":"會唔會係包機 送返外星人走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}